    course_description = '<div class="overview__text"> <p class="overview__title display-3" style="font-weight:bold;">Overview</p> <p> In today’s world of rapid change, innovative thinkers are in high demand. Innovative change agents can apply commercial, social and ethical knowledge as well as critical thinking skills to solve real-world problems.</p> <p> The Bachelor of Innovation with Honours develops skills in communication, digital engagement, problem solving, taking initiative and teamwork, enabling you to apply research and creativity skills across a range of contexts.</p> <p> The course includes an embedded industry research project to foster skills in research methodologies that can complement future industry research.</p> <p> The Bachelor of Innovation with Honours is a pathway from a range of Southern Cross undergraduate degrees for students who wish to build their knowledge in research and creative thinking.</p> </div>',
