f-access learning materials (approx. 6 hrs per week)</li> <li> Networking and mentoring support (approx. 1 hour per week)</li> </ul> <p> Note. The professional certificate consists of six modules, with each module having a duration of two weeks.</p> <p> In addition, students must complete all assessment items to a satisfactory standard.</p> <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="accordionRequirements"> </div> </div>',
